Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:11.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an8\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}おやすみ異世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:18.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,fx,{\an8\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}さようなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.13,0:22:18.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}入睡轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.30,0:22:22.76,ED-CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\an2\fad(500,500)\blur8\bord2}只要在想着你
